title = "[center]Thank You for Tending the Jade Spring[/center]"
copy = "Dear Steward. We would like to convey our appreciation for your hard work in helping to purify and reinvigorate Jade Spring. This place has endured over many long ages, but has grown weary and decrepit ever since the Jade Wind - at least until you and Ratchet came to walk these lands. You have proven yourself a gentle and worthy steward, and are welcome to decorate the garden as you please. 
[font_size=7] [/font_size]
